  "keyFeatures": [
    "Unified API for both browser automation and HTTP requests",
    "No WebDriver dependency — uses Chrome DevTools Protocol directly",
    "Cross-iframe element search without context switching",
    "Multi-tab operation without tab switching",
    "Built-in auto-wait and retry mechanisms",
    "INI-file based persistent configuration",
    "Integrated download management via DownloadKit",
    "Full-page screenshots including off-viewport content",
    "Shadow-root element support",
    "POM (Page Object Model) friendly design"
